# ============================================================================
# LOCAL DEV ONLY — demo, non-secret values. Safe to commit. NEVER use in production.
# Supplies the Compose interpolation vars the bundled base needs. Used via:
#   docker compose --env-file dev/dev.env -f docker-compose.yml -f dev/docker-compose.yml up -d --build
# The anon/service keys below are the well-known supabase-demo JWTs, signed by the
# demo GOTRUE_JWT_SECRET below — they validate against the local GoTrue, nothing else.
# ============================================================================
